<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Brevet Blanc — Calendrier de Révision</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;0,900;1,400&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --cream: #f5f0e8;
    --ink: #1a1612;
    --ink-light: #3d352b;
    --accent: #c84b2f;
    --accent2: #2d6a4f;
    --accent3: #1d4e89;
    --accent4: #7b4f9e;
    --accent5: #c17d11;
    --gold: #d4a017;
    --warm-gray: #8a7f72;
    --card-bg: #faf7f2;
    --border: #ddd5c5;
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    background: var(--cream);
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.7;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* ── HERO ── */
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    position: relative;
    background: var(--ink);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 20% 30%, rgba(200,75,47,0.18) 0%, transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 80% at 80% 70%, rgba(29,78,137,0.15) 0%, transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 40% at 50% 50%, rgba(212,160,23,0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .hero-noise {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    opacity: 0.04;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='n'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23n)'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
    background-size: 200px;
  }

  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    border: 1px solid rgba(200,75,47,0.4);
    padding: 0.4em 1.2em;
    border-radius: 100px;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease both;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 7rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--cream);
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.1s ease both;
  }

  .hero h1 em {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 1.3rem);
    color: rgba(245,240,232,0.55);
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.2s ease both;
  }

  .hero-dates {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.3s ease both;
  }

  .hero-date-pill {
    background: rgba(245,240,232,0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(245,240,232,0.15);
    color: var(--cream);
    padding: 0.5em 1.4em;
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .scroll-cue {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 2.5rem;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    color: rgba(245,240,232,0.3);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    animation: fadeUp 1s 0.6s ease both;
  }

  .scroll-line {
    width: 1px;
    height: 40px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(245,240,232,0.3), transparent);
    animation: scrollLine 1.5s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  /* ── NAV ── */
  .sticky-nav {
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    background: rgba(26,22,18,0.95);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(245,240,232,0.08);
    overflow-x: auto;
  }

  .sticky-nav::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }

  .nav-inner {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1rem;
  }

  .nav-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 1rem 1.2rem;
    color: rgba(245,240,232,0.45);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    white-space: nowrap;
    transition: color 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
    border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
  }

  .nav-item:hover { color: var(--cream); border-color: var(--accent); }
  .nav-item .dot { width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; }

  /* ── LAYOUT ── */
  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .section {
    padding: 5rem 0;
  }

  .section-header {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .section-tag {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    display: block;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  /* ── CALENDAR ── */
  .calendar-section {
    background: var(--ink);
    padding: 5rem 0;
  }

  .calendar-section .section-title { color: var(--cream); }
  .calendar-section .section-tag { color: var(--accent); }

  .calendar-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(320px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
  }

  .day-card {
    background: rgba(245,240,232,0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(245,240,232,0.1);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 1.75rem;
    transition: transform 0.25s ease, background 0.25s;
    cursor: default;
  }

  .day-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    background: rgba(245,240,232,0.07);
  }

  .day-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .day-number {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1;
    color: rgba(245,240,232,0.12);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .day-title-block { flex: 1; }

  .day-weekday {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--warm-gray);
  }

  .day-subject {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--cream);
    margin-top: 0.25rem;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .day-slots { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.6rem; }

  .slot {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .slot-time {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--warm-gray);
    padding-top: 0.15rem;
    min-width: 60px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .slot-text {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: rgba(245,240,232,0.7);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .day-goal {
    margin-top: 1.25rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    background: rgba(200,75,47,0.12);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
    border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: rgba(245,240,232,0.65);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* ── SUBJECTS ── */
  .subjects-section { background: var(--card-bg); }

  .subject-tabs {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .tab-btn {
    padding: 0.5em 1.3em;
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    cursor: pointer;
    border: 2px solid transparent;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--ink-light);
    border-color: var(--border);
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
  }

  .tab-btn.active, .tab-btn:hover {
    color: #fff;
    border-color: transparent;
  }

  .subject-content { display: none; }
  .subject-content.active { display: block; animation: fadeIn 0.3s ease; }

  .topic-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(260px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .topic-card {
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    transition: box-shadow 0.2s;
  }

  .topic-card:hover { box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(26,22,18,0.08); }

  .topic-card h4 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .topic-card h4::before {
    content: '';
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .topic-card ul {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.3rem;
  }

  .topic-card ul li {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--ink-light);
    padding-left: 1em;
    position: relative;
  }

  .topic-card ul li::before {
    content: '—';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--border);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
  }

  /* ── FORMULAS / DATES ── */
  .reference-section { background: var(--cream); }

  .ref-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .ref-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  .ref-block {
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .ref-block h3 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.6rem;
  }

  .formula-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 0.65rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .formula-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  .formula-label {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--warm-gray);
    min-width: 140px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .formula-val {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-weight: 500;
    background: var(--cream);
    padding: 0.2em 0.6em;
    border-radius: 6px;
  }

  .date-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }

  .date-table tr { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .date-table tr:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  .date-table td {
    padding: 0.6rem 0;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    vertical-align: middle;
  }

  .date-table td:first-child {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 500;
    padding-right: 1rem;
    white-space: nowrap;
    width: 100px;
  }

  /* ── CHECKLIST ── */
  .checklist-section { background: var(--ink); padding: 5rem 0; }
  .checklist-section .section-title { color: var(--cream); }
  .checklist-section .section-tag { color: var(--accent); }

  .checklist-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
  }

  .check-item {
    background: rgba(245,240,232,0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(245,240,232,0.1);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }

  .check-item:hover { background: rgba(245,240,232,0.07); }

  .check-duration {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--accent);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .check-label {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--cream);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .check-note {
    font-size: 0.74rem;
    color: var(--warm-gray);
  }

  /* ── METHODS ── */
  .methods-section { background: var(--card-bg); }

  .methods-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
  }

  .method-card {
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
  }

  .method-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(26,22,18,0.1);
  }

  .method-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 4px;
  }

  .method-card h3 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .method-card p, .method-card ol {
    font-size: 0.84rem;
    color: var(--ink-light);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .method-card ol {
    padding-left: 1.2em;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.3rem;
  }

  /* ── EMC KEYWORDS ── */
  .keywords-wrap {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .kw-pill {
    padding: 0.4em 1em;
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    background: var(--cream);
    border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--ink);
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .kw-pill:hover { background: var(--ink); color: var(--cream); border-color: var(--ink); }

  /* ── FOOTER ── */
  footer {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: rgba(245,240,232,0.3);
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(245,240,232,0.08);
  }

  /* ── COLORS per subject ── */
  .c-fr { color: #c84b2f; }
  .c-ma { color: #1d4e89; }
  .c-hi { color: #7b4f9e; }
  .c-ge { color: #2d6a4f; }
  .c-em { color: #c17d11; }
  .c-ph { color: #0077b6; }
  .c-sv { color: #40916c; }
  .c-te { color: #6c3483; }

  .bg-fr { background: #c84b2f; }
  .bg-ma { background: #1d4e89; }
  .bg-hi { background: #7b4f9e; }
  .bg-ge { background: #2d6a4f; }
  .bg-em { background: #c17d11; }
  .bg-ph { background: #0077b6; }
  .bg-sv { background: #40916c; }
  .bg-te { background: #6c3483; }

  .dot-fr { background: #c84b2f; }
  .dot-ma { background: #1d4e89; }
  .dot-hi { background: #7b4f9e; }
  .dot-ge { background: #2d6a4f; }
  .dot-em { background: #c17d11; }
  .dot-ph { background: #0077b6; }
  .dot-sv { background: #40916c; }
  .dot-te { background: #6c3483; }

  .topic-card.fr h4::before { background: #c84b2f; }
  .topic-card.ma h4::before { background: #1d4e89; }
  .topic-card.hi h4::before { background: #7b4f9e; }
  .topic-card.ge h4::before { background: #2d6a4f; }
  .topic-card.em h4::before { background: #c17d11; }
  .topic-card.ph h4::before { background: #0077b6; }
  .topic-card.sv h4::before { background: #40916c; }
  .topic-card.te h4::before { background: #6c3483; }

  .method-fr::before { background: #c84b2f; }
  .method-ma::before { background: #1d4e89; }
  .method-hi::before { background: #7b4f9e; }
  .method-em::before { background: #c17d11; }
  .method-sc::before { background: #0077b6; }

  /* ── ANIMATIONS ── */
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  @keyframes fadeIn {
    from { opacity: 0; }
    to { opacity: 1; }
  }

  @keyframes scrollLine {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 0.3; transform: scaleY(1); }
    50% { opacity: 1; transform: scaleY(0.6); }
  }

  .reveal {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(30px);
    transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease;
  }

  .reveal.visible {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  /* ── DIVIDER ── */
  .ruled-divider {
    width: 60px;
    height: 3px;
    background: var(--accent);
    border-radius: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .section-intro {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--warm-gray);
    max-width: 560px;
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .calendar-grid, .topic-grid, .methods-grid, .checklist-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .ref-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .nav-inner { padding: 0 0.5rem; }
    .nav-item { padding: 1rem 0.8rem; font-size: 0.72rem; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ══ HERO ══ -->
<header class="hero">
  <div class="hero-noise"></div>
  <div class="hero-badge">Collège · 3ème</div>
  <h1>Brevet<br><em>Blanc</em></h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">Calendrier complet de révision · Toutes matières</p>
  <div class="hero-dates">
    <span class="hero-date-pill">📅 Du 6 juin</span>
    <span class="hero-date-pill">📅 Au 17 juin</span>
    <span class="hero-date-pill">📚 12 jours intenses</span>
  </div>
  <div class="scroll-cue">
    <span>Explorer</span>
    <div class="scroll-line"></div>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- ══ NAV ══ -->
<nav class="sticky-nav">
  <div class="nav-inner">
    <a class="nav-item" href="#calendrier"><span class="dot dot-fr"></span>Calendrier</a>
    <a class="nav-item" href="#programme"><span class="dot dot-ma"></span>Programme</a>
    <a class="nav-item" href="#formules"><span class="dot dot-hi"></span>Formules</a>
    <a class="nav-item" href="#dates-hist"><span class="dot dot-ge"></span>Dates</a>
    <a class="nav-item" href="#checklist"><span class="dot dot-em"></span>Checklist</a>
    <a class="nav-item" href="#methodes"><span class="dot dot-ph"></span>Méthodes</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- ══ CALENDRIER ══ -->
<section class="calendar-section" id="calendrier">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header reveal">
      <span class="section-tag">Planning</span>
      <h2 class="section-title" style="color:var(--cream);">Calendrier Jour<br>par Jour</h2>
      <div class="ruled-divider" style="margin-top:1.25rem;"></div>
      <p class="section-intro" style="color:var(--warm-gray);">12 jours de révision structurés du 6 au 17 juin. Chaque journée est divisée en trois créneaux.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="calendar-grid">

      <!-- J1 -->
      <div class="day-card reveal">
        <div class="day-header">
          <div class="day-number">6</div>
          <div class="day-title-block">
            <div class="day-weekday">Samedi · Jour 1</div>
            <div class="day-subject">Organisation + Bases de Français</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="day-slots">
          <div class="slot"><span class="slot-time">Matin</span><span class="slot-text">Prépare tes cahiers, fiches, sujets d'annales et planning. Classe les matières.</span></div>
          <div class="slot"><span class="slot-time">Après-midi</span><span class="slot-text">Français : classes grammaticales, fonctions, phrases simples et complexes.</span></div>
          <div class="slot"><span class="slot-time">Soir</span><span class="slot-text">Dictée + 20 questions de grammaire. Note toutes tes erreurs.</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="day-goal">🎯 Objectif : savoir ce que tu maîtrises déjà et ce que tu dois travailler.</div>
